<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="from-prep">from <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /frəm/    美 /frəm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示起点] 从；从...起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fly from London to Paris 
从伦敦飞到巴黎</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We work from Monday to Friday.
我们从星期一到星期五上班。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[表示来源] 自；从...中：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a quotation from the Bible 
引自《圣经》的话</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Where do you come from? 
你是哪里人？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[表示原料] 由：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The paper is made from wood. 
这纸是用木头造的。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[表示原因、动机] 由于；出于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>suffer from a cold 
患感冒</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>[表示情况、状态的转变] 从：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>translate from Chinese into Russian 
把汉语译成俄语</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>From a shop assistant he became a president.
他从店员变成了总统。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>[表示脱离、离开] 离：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>take five from ten 
10减去5</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why was he absent from school yesterday?
他昨天为什么没上学？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Shirley, a real book lover, often brings home many books to read <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the library.  （2011 重庆改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. from  </p></div>